in carbon abundance among\nthe most metal-poor Draco stars. We identify a potential carbon-rich extremely\nmetal-poor star in our sample. This candidate will require follow up\nobservations for confirmation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Mar 2013 16:55:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-14"}
