_1,\\ldots,m_k)$ if and only if $(m_1,\\ldots,m_k)\\succ (n_1,\\ldots,n_k)$,\nwhere $\\sum_{i=1}^kn_i=\\sum_{i=1}^km_i$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Mar 2013 17:32:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-14"}
