he pump pulse. We also find that the imaginary part of\nthe dielectric function can be negative, particularly for the parallel\npolarization of pump and probe fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Mar 2013 18:54:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-19"}
