 the\nrapid speed increases of the upward plasmoids, the individual loop shrinkages,\nand the overall loop-top descent, suggestive of an intimate relation of the\nenergy release rate and reconnection outflow speed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2013 00:43:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-04"}
