er with $^{40}$Ca in the C/Si zone, and/or to the strong\ndepletion of $^{40}$Ca by neutron captures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2013 08:13:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
