h cosmologies at $(\\omega/H)_0 < 8.6 \\times\n10^{-10}$ with 95% confidence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2013 11:22:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2013 02:56:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-04"}
