ce and phase by tracking\ntrajectories, parametrized by the relevant biophysical parameter, in\npre-constructed attribute diagrams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2013 15:45:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-15"}
